Thank you.

Great! I assume Zootopia has something to do with animals but can you tell anything more about it?

I would personally recommend it for someone or a get together of people who would enjoy a good laugh. It is about Bunnyburrow a newly appointed member of the police department in zootopia. she is trying to catch a con artist the red fox played by Jason Bateman.

Interesting...

I would go say it would be best for both genders! but you can watch it individually with them for twice the bonding or at the same time!
